 when we have the mandala of our practice, if we are supplicating the objects of refuge,

00:19:36.040 --> 00:19:46.590
 then as far as the mandala, right, that would have the center, the east, the south, the west, the

00:19:46.590 --> 00:19:48.040
 north,

